":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ff81a21a781dca78b1bd767103b6795c8a62ef","tid":1834392,"uid":114580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:54:35.000Z","msg":"借位幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Twitter戰線]肺炎打大佬CCP，唔打卒仔 - 疫症宣傳整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1836358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1836358</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"72d5a2dfe62d7a8d68708937b344828b3ba711ab","tid":1834392,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6D99N1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6D99N1.jpg&h=7b3a2dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLwS7zG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLwS7zG.png&h=3526869f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb3826495302b6a2a990972aa4205a8c812a23eb","tid":1834392,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72d5a2dfe62d7a8d68708937b344828b3ba711ab","tid":1834392,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6D99N1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6D99N1.jpg&h=7b3a2dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLwS7zG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLwS7zG.png&h=3526869f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"最尾幅圖 姐係樓下冇水自己都會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慘"},{"pid":"fb43497aaaea7a16fbd96cc493bbfd0b5afe1eba","tid":1834392,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"2536de8546487a081d0488f920fb547d889764f7","tid":1834392,"uid":130225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d1946a9d24f6abf0be3a88ca1a92317ff0e8c37","tid":1834392,"uid":34241,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"41e7bbfbd7c5ab4d0533007bcedb6eff74ad4585","tid":1834392,"uid":58287,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"52d0c2c686e9cb6f491da953a2b5b1f49dfecc78","tid":1834392,"uid":158499,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"隔氣點會枯乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年係話因為佢棟大廈用U型去水位所以有，但詳情好似唔係樓主嗰嘅咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T17:05:02.000Z","msg":"根據當局與淘大花園居民的面 談，涉及廁所內<br />\n散發臭味的投訴十分普遍，顯示接駁一些單位的 U 形<br />\n聚水器可能未有發揮其應有功用。由於水廁、洗手盆、<br />\n浴缸是常用的，所以與其相連的 U 形聚水器大部分時<br />\n間應是有貯水的，並應能發揮隔氣功用。不過，由於大<br />\n部 分 住 戶 清 潔 浴 室 地 面 時，慣 性 以 拖 把 抹 地 而 不 是 用 水<br />\n沖洗，所以大部分連接地台排水口的 U 形聚水器很可<br />\n能因乾涸而未能發揮隔氣作用。事實上，當局曾在 E<br />\n座 一 個 單 位 內 進 行 測 試，發 現 當 浴 室 的 抽 氣 扇 啟 動 後 ，<br />\n空 氣 會 從 污 水 管 經 地 台 排 水 口 倒 流 進 入 浴 室。我 們 推 測<br />\n這氣流可能把存於污水管內的帶病毒液滴散發至浴室<br />\n內，而 浴 室 的 抽 氣 扇 亦 可 能 把 這 些液滴排放至分隔相鄰<br />\n單位的天井，最後帶病毒的滴液通過窗戶進入其他單位<br />\n<br />\nquote: <a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/info/sars/pdf/amoy_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fsars%2Fpdf%2Famoy_c.pdf&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=70e0cd98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/info/sars/pdf/amoy_c.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"你03年個時幾歲?<br />\n定係已經唔記得左?"},{"pid":"7708e39d8ad783d799446521b9eec3943b5d8678","tid":1834392,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"73eb866613a3553c8229ad6411c4d160a1dd45e5","tid":1834392,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:57:02.000Z",